[30;1m186 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m187 | [0m[35m* `psrp.AsyncPowerShell` - runs a PowerShell command through asyncio[0m

[30;1m211 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m212 | [0m[35m* `psrp.AsyncPowerShell` - runs a PowerShell command through asyncio[0m

[30;1m206 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m207 | [0m[35m### Pipeline[0m
[30;1m208 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m209 | [0m[35mA Pipeline is used to execute a command or script on the Runspace Pool it is associated with.[0m
[30;1m210 | [0m[35mThere are 4 types of pipelines that can be used:[0m
[30;1m211 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m212 | [0m[35m* `psrp.AsyncPowerShell` - runs a PowerShell command through asyncio[0m
